Description: FluentPDO - PHP 8.1+ Edition with modern features
 FluentPDO is a modernized PHP SQL query builder library using PDO with a smart
 join builder that automatically creates table joins. This version (3.x) requires
 PHP 8.1+ and includes modern type declarations, strict typing, and enhanced
 features.
 .
 Key features:
  - Smart Join Builder: Automatically creates JOINs based on column references
  - Fluent Interface: Method chaining for building queries
  - PDO Integration: Built on top of PDO for database portability
  - Type Safety: Modern PHP 8.1+ with strict typing throughout
  - Union Types: Uses modern PHP union types where appropriate
